This is a funny one. Small remark:
- I think the case of 0 urinals is a bit different from 1 or more urinals, so I think that a test with output 0 should have an equivalent validator with output 0.

Goal
* Please rewrite the last paragraph as follows:

Given a string [[s]] containing {{X}} and {{O}} which represent an occupied urinal and an available one respectively, how many urinals can you comfortably use?

Input
* Please rewrite as follows:
<<Line 1>> String [[s]] containing {{X}} and {{O}} which represent an occupied urinal and an available one respectively

Output
* Please delete "A".

* Please change "can you" to "you can".

* Please delete "?".

Constraints
* Please fix the typo: "Lenght" => "Length".

Stub generator
* Last line: Please delete "A".

Thanks.
